Testng ---Java Unit testing framework
It can generate very good html reports
it gives lot of annotations
You can set sequence/priority of test cases
You can execute test cases multiple times with different data
Purpose -- design test cases in a systematic way

testng is open source--free
testng is available in form of jar files

install testng in eclipse:

http://beust.com/eclipse

go to eclipse-->help-->new software-->copy/paste this url "http://beust.com/eclipse"
or
go to eclipse-->help-->new software-->copy/paste-->http://dl.bintray.com/testng-team/testng-eclipse-release/

https://www.lambdatest.com/blog/how-to-install-testng-in-eclipse-step-by-step-guide/